alexa-esp32
Copyright 2026 HomeControl Contributors

This library is a C++ port of alexapy, adapted for the ESP32 Arduino platform.
The API client logic, authentication flow, and endpoint usage were derived from
the alexapy Python package by line-by-line study and reimplementation in C++.

